Package application

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertBox
    AlertBox class utilizes an internal display method to alert user of something
    AllResultsController
    Controller class for AllResults.fxml which calls initialize() prior to launching GUI.
    AllResultsDefaultController
    Controller class for AllResults.fxml which calls initialize() prior to launching GUI.
    ConfirmBox
    ConfirmBox class utilizes an internal display method to confirm a user action
    Database
    The Database class will be home to all methods which pertain to the local MySQL database for this project.
    Main
    Application scrapes text from a website and displays top10 (and all) word occurrences to a JavaFX GUI.
    MainController
    Controller class for Main.fxml which calls initialize() prior to launching GUI.
    MainDefaultController
    Controller class for Main.fxml which calls initialize() prior to launching GUI.
    QuestionBox
    ConfirmBox class utilizes an internal display method to confirm a user action
    WebScrape
    A Class that will scrape text from given URL, add to a HashMap(of String, Integer) with all word entries and, finally, add each key/value pair to an ArrayList(of Word (Word implements Comparable(of Word))) so the ArrayList can be sorted by number of occurrences.
    Word
    Word Class objects are created from HashMap(of String, Integer) (key=word, value=frequency) and implements Comparable(of Word) so ArrayList(Word) can be sorted and overrides toString() to print results to console.
    WordManager
